<p><b>  Recommendations that fall outside the scope of the universal periodic review 
</b></p>
<p>16. France considers that the recommendations concerning its contribution to 
international official development assistance do not fall within the scope of the universal 
periodic review. It therefore does not consider it necessary to respond to the following 
recommendations: 
</p>
<p>120.52, 120.53, 120.54. 
</p>
